videos.description: Kemba Walker beats everyone down the court and makes an easy layup in transition in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Kemba shows speed and scores) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kemba shows speed and scores

videos.description: The Nuggets pass all around the key before Torrey Craig connects with Gary Harris who drills a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Nuggets' great ball movement leads to triple) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nuggets' great ball movement leads to triple

videos.description: Dwight Howard drives from the outside to inside the paint where he scores and draws the foul for a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Howard gets inside for bucket and-1) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howard gets inside for bucket and-1

videos.description: Emmanuel Mudiay tosses the ball down low to Torrey Craig who rises up for a two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Mudiay dishes to Craig for slam) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mudiay dishes to Craig for slam

videos.description: Jamal Murray drives down the lane and throws down a monster one-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Murray explodes to the rim for jam) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray explodes to the rim for jam

videos.description: Dwight Howard can't stop Nikola Jokic who drills a deep 3-pointer from the top of the key.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Jokic sinks wide-open triple) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jokic sinks wide-open triple

videos.description: Nikola Jokic grabs the board and finds Gary Harris who races to the rim and hits the layup for a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Harris scores on the run for and-1) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris scores on the run for and-1

videos.description: Jamal Murray shows off the handles on Dwight Howard and later knocks in a two 3-pointers. By the end of the third quarter, he has 18 points against the Hornets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Murray heating up in the third quarter) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray heating up in the third quarter

videos.description: Torrey Craig gets in the air to block Cody Zeller dunk attempt and he nearly flips all the way around before crashing to the ground on his back.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Craig hits the deck hard on block) 2018/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Craig hits the deck hard on block
